title: Ricardo Arana
text:

I work full time at H&M in Santa Barabara and I plan on tutoring next semester at CSUCI. I am currently open to any internship opportunities in the computer science/cybersecurity/engineering field.

title: About Me
text: Hello, I am 22 years old and I live in Santa Barbara. I commute and attend school full time at CSUCI and work full time. I began my educational career at Santa Barbara City College and earned AS degrees in Computer Science, Physics, and Mathematics. I like to play spikeball on my days off from work and school. I have a dog named Riley, she is a German Ghephard & Husky mix and goes everywhere I go.
